# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.0.2] - 2026-02-15

### Added
  - PCAP and PCAPNG file reading
  - `NxPacket` struct for unified packet representation
  - `PacketSource` trait for capture abstraction
  - Basic CLI with `read` command
  - Integration tests with sample PCAP files
  
  ### Dependencies
  - Added pcap-file 3.0.0-rc1
  - Added thiserror 2.0.18
  - Added clap 4.5
  - Added time 0.3

## [0.0.1] - 2026-01-31

### Added
- Initial project structure
- Workspace setup with `onx` crate
- MIT OR Apache-2.0 dual licensing
- Placeholder binary for crate name reservation

### Notes
This is a name reservation release. Core functionality will be implemented
in v0.1.0.
